 frames to a short list of candidates</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45  1:00 </strong>  Next steps  I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" background_color_2=\"#ffffff\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"on\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-top:20px;\" disabled=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/InounbCON-level.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_width=\"1px\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" disabled=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_text background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"25px|25px|25px|25px\" disabled=\"off\"]<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>The month-long advisoryengagement ($6K plus travel)</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">This is a popular engagement with startups that are looking to accelerate their strategic marketing efforts and get a months worth of hand-on learning with me. The goal here is to assess your problem areas, create an action plan and work through the first few weeks of implementing the plan. The way it works is I spend a day with the team to kick off the project, and then spend a half-day to a day with the team every week for a month. At the end we will have worked through a thorny strategy problem and Ive trained the team on how to move forward without me.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"></span></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me\" background_layout=\"light\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#2b2b2b\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px\" disabled=\"off\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Consulting','','inherit','closed','closed','','82-revision-v1','','','2017-01-31 16:01:42','2017-01-31 16:01:42','',82,'http://april.dev/index.php/2017/01/31/82-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2017-01-31 16:02:36','2017-01-31 16:02:36','[et_pb_section background_image=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/InounbCON-level.jpg\" transparent_background=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" admin_label=\"section\" disabled=\"off\" global_module=\"86\"][et_pb_row make