le=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>11:00 &ndash; 11:30</b> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></h4>\n<h4 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span class=\"s2\">Value &ndash; we then work through the value that is mapped to the&nbsp;</span>unique attributes</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>11:30 - 12:00</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Positionstorming &ndash; working with the 4 styles of framing as a guide we will brainstorm a long list of potential frames for consideration</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:15 &ndash; 12:45</strong>&nbsp;</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Creating the short list. We will narrow down the long list of potential frames to a short list of candidates</span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\"><strong>12:45 &ndash; 1:00 </strong></span></h4>\n<h4><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: #353535;\">Next steps &ndash; I will walk you through how to validate and test the candidates to come to a winning frame.</span></h4>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" admin_label=\"Button\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#000000\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px;||width:170px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" background_color_2=\"#ffffff\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax