</span><span class=\"s2\"><b>($100 - $300 per person) </b></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-size: medium;\">Occasionally I do a group workshop where I cover the basics of product framing and positioning and introduce a process you can use to find your own products best frame. Tickets prices depend on the size of the group. If you want to organize one in your town, drop me a line.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"></p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_text][et_pb_button admin_label=\"Button\" button_url=\"#\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Contact Me \" background_layout=\"light\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"20\" button_text_color=\"#191919\" button_use_icon=\"on\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" custom_css_main_element=\"margin-left:25px;||bottom:25px;||width:170px;\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" src=\"http://april.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Inboundcon-backstage-3.jpg\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_width=\"1px\" border_style=\"solid\" disabled=\"off\"] [/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"off\" custom_width_px=\"1080px\" custom_width_percent=\"80%\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" gutter_width=\"3\" custom_margin=\"|||\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"on\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"on\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"on\" paralla